\v 1 \add вүҲAfter a while when\add* DavidВҰ195287 was living in his house, \add *he\add* said to the prophetВҰ195294 NatanВҰ195293, вҖңLook, \add here\add* I am living in a \add вүҲpalace\add* \add made\add* of cedarВҰ195299, \add вүҲbut\add* the box \add containing\add* Yahweh's agreement is \add kept\add* \add вүҲin a tent\add*.вҖқ
\v 2 вҖң\add вүҲGo add andВҰ195307 do what you're planning\add*,вҖқ NatanВҰ195308 \add вүҲreplied\add*, вҖңbecause God is with you.вҖқ
