\v 16 Then kingВҰ195573 DavidВҰ195574 wentВҰ195572 in and satВҰ195575 \add вүҲin frontВҰ195576\add* of Yahweh, and \add вүҲasked\add*, вҖңWho am I, Yahweh GodВҰ195583, and what is my \add вүҲfamily\add*, that you've broughtВҰ195587 me \add вүҲto this point\add*?
