\v 20 YahwehВҰ195643, there's no one else like you, and no godВҰ195647 except you, \add вүҲas we've all heardВҰ195652 for ourselves\add*.
\v 21 \add вүҲThere's no other countryВҰ195658\add* like your people YisraelВҰ195657вҖ”the only nationВҰ195658 in the world where \add you\add* God, rescued the people in order to make them your own. That made you famous andВҰ195655 also feared, as you drove the people groups out ahead of your people who you ransomed out of EgyptВҰ195678.
\v 22 You took your people YisraelВҰ195686 to be your people forever, andВҰ195681 you, YahwehВҰ195694, became our godВҰ195697.
