\v 24 May your reputation be established andВҰ195718 increase forever, as \add people\add* say, вҖҳArmy commander YahwehВҰ195725, Yisrael's godВҰ195727, is god over Yisrael.вҖҷ And your servantВҰ195734 David'sВҰ195733 family has been established \add вүҲas you've watched\add*
\v 25 because you, GodВҰ195741, \add вүҲhave revealed to yourВҰ195756 servant that you will give me a dynasty\add*. That's why I'm \add brave enough\add* to pray to you.
\v 26 \add вүҲYes,\add* YahwehВҰ195759, you are God andВҰ195764 you've promisedВҰ195764 these goodВҰ195768 thingsВҰ195768 to \add me,\add* yourВҰ195767 servantВҰ195767.
\v 27 ThenВҰ195771 you've now decided to bless your servant'sВҰ195777 family to be forever \add вүҲin front of you\add*, because you, YahwehВҰ195784, have blessed \add us\add* andВҰ195771 so \add we'll\add* be blessed forever.
