\p
\v 1 \add вүҲSometime afterwardsВҰ195791\add*, DavidВҰ195795 \add вүҲattacked and defeatedВҰ195794\add* the PhilistinesВҰ195798, \add вүҲsubduingВҰ195799\add* them, and he \add вүҲcaptured the Philistine city of GatВҰ195803 and its surrounding villagesВҰ195804\add*.
\v 2 ThenВҰ195808 he \add вүҲattacked and defeatedВҰ195808\add* Moav, and the Moabites became servants to DavidВҰ195815вҖ”\add вүҲtaking him\add* \add regular\add* tributeВҰ195817.
